  },
  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-special\">Somnal Dust</span>, the accumulated decay of time and memories, is found in the wrecks of derelict freighters caught within the loop.<br><br>Locate derelicts with the use of an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Emergency Signal Scanner</span>, purchaseable from a Space Station <span class=\"name name-special\">Scrap Dealer</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">索姆纳尔灰尘</span>是时间和记忆衰变后的物质，在被循环捕获的荒废货船残骸中发现。<br><br>使用从空间站<span class=\"name name-special\">废品收购者</span>处购买的<span class=\"name name-technology\">紧急信号扫描仪</span>定位荒废的货船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">睡眠塵</span>為時間與記憶的腐朽積累物，可在受困於迴圈的廢棄貨船殘骸中找到。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">緊急訊號掃描器</span>找到棄船，接收器可向太空站上的<span class=\"name name-special\">廢料商人</span>購買。"
  },
  "PinObjectiveMessage": {
    "English": "Find <span class=\"name name-special\">Somnal Dust</span> in the wrecks of deep-space derelict freighters caught within the loop<br>Locate derelicts with an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Emergency Signal Scanner</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "在陷入循环的深空荒废货船中寻找<span class=\"name name-special\">索姆纳尔灰尘</span><br>使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">紧急信号扫描仪</span>定位太空残骸",
    "TraditionalChinese": "在受困於迴圈的深空廢棄貨船殘骸中找到<span class=\"name name-special\">睡眠塵</span><br>使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">緊急訊號掃描器</span>找到棄船"
  },
